{"body": "Do you mean `app.config.active_record.use_schema_cache_dump` ?\nIf so, I guess we should add ActiveRecord::Base.use_schema_cache_dump too.\n\n```ruby\n 71     initializer \"active_record.set_configs\" do |app|\n 72       ActiveSupport.on_load(:active_record) do\n 73         app.config.active_record.each do |k,v|\n 74           send \"#{k}=\", v\n 75         end\n 76       end\n 77     end\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/7429745", "created_at": "2012-08-01T15:01:52Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7224#issuecomment-7429745", "updated_at": "2012-08-01T15:12:28Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7224, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/kennyj", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F54ecc28e9508fcf28363014b0d1b4eb8.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/received_events", "gravatar_id": "1f0b221851379759360d7130dabdfa53", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "kennyj", "type": "User", "id": 13426, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kennyj/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237fe13bd3543c15100bc6e"}, "id": 7429745, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7224"}
